data.description: The character still remains in this 1945 Bungalow. Original hardwood floors with cypress molding and built in window box. Come see this adorable 2 bedroom home.  The sun porch was used as a 3rd bedroom but would be perfect for home office, or extra living space.  There is plenty of storage with the walk up attic. Kitchen comes complete with all appliances, and movable island.  A 3 car detached garage, with 2 doors on the front and a 3rd that enters from the back. Above the garage is extra storage if the walk up attic isn't enough.  Nice size yard that backs up to a stream.  This home is close enough to walk uptown or to school but has a very private, rural feel to it.  Make your appointment today.  Agent is a relative to seller.  Please submit offers by Thursday 4/11 by 9:00 am
